  "body": "<!--NOTE: -->\r\n<!--- General questions should go to the discord chat instead of the issue tracker.-->\r\n\r\n**Describe the bug**\r\n\r\nCoercing values in if statements can be problematic if the variable can be a 0 which should be truthy:\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nlet num: number | null;\r\nif (num) {}\r\n```\r\n\r\nRequire\r\n\r\n```ts\r\nlet num: number | null;\r\nif (num !== null && num > 0) {}\r\n```\r\n\r\nCheck: https://eslint.org/docs/rules/no-implicit-coercion",
